We accept the death of others, but not our own. You have to die someday. Keep it in your mind.
<br>Q: Depression can be caused if say to self all the time, I am going to die?
<br>A: That is non-acceptance.
<br>Q: When someone says he&#8217;s not afraid of death but of the maybe painful process of dying, painful death, is his real fear actually fear of death itself?
<br>A: Yes. <span class=date>10/26/76</span>
